Title: Relates to requiring the commissioner of the department of civil service to prepare a report on mental health practitioner classification
Summary: Relates to requiring the commissioner of the department of civil service to prepare a report on mental health practitioner classification.
ActClause: AN ACT to require the commissioner of the department of civil service to prepare a report regarding the classification of mental health practitioners
